    <h1>Return on Ad Spend (ROAS)</h1>
    <p class="description">A ratio that tells you how much revenue you earn for every dollar spent on advertising. <strong>ROAS = Revenue / Ad Spend.</strong> Simple to calculate, but context-dependent to interpret correctly.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
